Our People – Capula




















































 
















AboutHistorySenior Management TeamVertical MarketsNuclearDefenceFuel Production & ReprocessingNew BuildResearch & DevelopmentDecommissioningWaste Management & StoragePower GenerationRenewablesPower TransmissionWaterOil and GasProcess IndustriesCapabilitiesSystems     Substation Automation – IMPERIUM     Material Tracking     Boiler Control     DCS     Telemetry     SCADA     PLC     Safety SystemsService     Support ContractsAsset Management24/7 SupportLong Term Support ContractsObsolescence Management     System Upgrades     Technical Audits     Cyber Security     Panel Build     Security Management     Repairs Service     Consultancy     Health Checks     Migration     TrainingSoftware Solutions     OPUS Building Management Performance     Transmission Networks – IMPERIUM     Situational Awareness     Network VisibilityCase StudiesPartnersMediaWorking At CapulaOur PeopleProfilesDeveloping TalentGraduate ProgrammeVacanciesContactSearch









 















 Our PeopleAt Capula we are extremely proud of what we do and how well we do it. We are hard working, but at the same time, we’re friendly with a good team spirit. The jobs that we do are challenging and require able managers and robust technical solutions. We like our staff to be flexible and encourage them to take responsibility, with career progression according to ability to do the job.
Our systems are primarily based upon PLC, SCADA, and hardware components, with our real-time solutions based upon Real-time Business Intelligence (RtBI). But we also use a range of other software technologies, such as Oracle, SQL Server, VB, Java and other web-based technologies.
To see what job opportunities we’re currently offering, click through the links to the left of your screen. We are always interested in hearing from skilled individuals, so if you don’t find an advertised vacancy to suit your talents but would like to notify us of your availability, use the form to the right to forward your details to us.





