Vertical Markets – Capula






















































 
















AboutHistorySenior Management TeamVertical MarketsNuclearDefenceFuel Production & ReprocessingNew BuildResearch & DevelopmentDecommissioningWaste Management & StoragePower GenerationRenewablesPower TransmissionWaterOil and GasProcess IndustriesCapabilitiesSystems     Substation Automation – IMPERIUM     Material Tracking     Boiler Control     DCS     Telemetry     SCADA     PLC     Safety SystemsService     Support ContractsAsset Management24/7 SupportLong Term Support ContractsObsolescence Management     System Upgrades     Technical Audits     Cyber Security     Panel Build     Security Management     Repairs Service     Consultancy     Health Checks     Migration     TrainingSoftware Solutions     OPUS Building Management Performance     Transmission Networks – IMPERIUM     Situational Awareness     Network VisibilityCase StudiesPartnersMediaWorking At CapulaOur PeopleProfilesDeveloping TalentGraduate ProgrammeVacanciesContactSearch









 













Vertical Markets
We have a wealth of expertise in energy-related markets ranging from nuclear, power, renewables, transmission and distribution, water, oil & gas through to other energy intensive industries.
Whilst each of our clients is unique, with specific strategic and operational objectives, they have common characteristics and regulatory constraints that we understand through specialising in these markets.
Our clients manage complex assets with the need for smarter ways to use real-time information and advanced controls to improve performance, reliability and environmental compliance.
They are looking for ways to reduce their carbon footprint, whether directly as energy producers or as high-energy users.  For each, they must do this safely and securely, with confidence in the data integrity of our solutions.
In the following sections, you will find overviews of the main market sectors for which we design, deliver and support our mission critical solutions.
Also, check out the News and Case Studies sections for specific stories about our projects.





Nuclear
Power Generation
Renewables
Power Transmission
Water
Oil & Gas
Process Industries
 

